    (55.55, 71.33),

    (52.09, 49.14),

# Plot the shape

plt.fill(x, y, alpha=0.3)
plt.title('SVG Path Shape')
plt.xlabel('X')
plt.ylabel('Y')
plt.grid(True)
plt.axis('equal')
plt.show()
